imdb.plot outline: A wonderful portrayal of what it is like to give up your life for something you love. The series follows two of the top synchronized swimming teams in the country as they rival to the top. The sport has never been harder, and Santa Clara and Walnut Creek are the best! Fans of dance moms rejoice, here comes dance moms two, but in water!
